	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَإِذَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> قِيلَ لَهُمۡ تَعَالَوۡاْ إِلَىٰ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ وَإِلَى ٱلرَّسُولِ قَالُواْ </div><div><a data-content='كافينا' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>حَسۡبُنَا</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَجَدۡنَا عَلَيۡهِ ءَابَآءَنَآۚ أَوَلَوۡ كَانَ ءَابَآؤُهُمۡ لَا </div><div>يَعۡلَمُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>شَيۡ‍ٔٗا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَلَا يَهۡتَدُونَ ٤٠١ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ </div><div><a data-content='الزموها واحفظوها من المعاصي' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>عَلَيۡكُمۡ أَنفُسَكُمۡۖ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يَضُرُّكُم مَّن ضَلَّ إِذَا ٱهۡتَدَيۡتُمۡۚ إِلَى ٱللَّهِ مَرۡجِعُكُمۡ </div><div>جَمِيعٗا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَيُنَبِّئُكُم</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ ٥٠١ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ </div><div>شَهَٰدَةُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بَيۡنِكُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> إِذَا حَضَرَ أَحَدَكُمُ ٱلۡمَوۡتُ حِينَ ٱلۡوَصِيَّةِ ٱثۡنَانِ </div><div>ذَوَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>عَدۡلٖ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مِّنكُمۡ أَوۡ ءَاخَرَانِ مِنۡ غَيۡرِكُمۡ إِنۡ أَنتُمۡ </div><div><a data-content='سافرتم فيها' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ضَرَبۡتُمۡ فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَأَصَٰبَتۡكُم</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مُّصِيبَةُ ٱلۡمَوۡتِۚ تَحۡبِسُونَهُمَا مِنۢ بَعۡدِ </div><div>ٱلصَّلَوٰةِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَيُقۡسِمَانِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> بِٱللَّهِ إِنِ ٱرۡتَبۡتُمۡ <a data-content='لا نأخذ بقسَمنا كذبا عرضا دنيويا' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>لَا نَشۡتَرِي بِهِۦ ثَمَنٗا</a> وَلَوۡ كَانَ </div><div>ذَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>قُرۡبَىٰ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَلَا نَكۡتُمُ شَهَٰدَةَ ٱللَّهِ إِنَّآ إِذٗا لَّمِنَ ٱلۡأٓثِمِينَ ٦٠١ فَإِنۡ </div><div>عُثِرَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>عَلَىٰٓ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَنَّهُمَا ٱسۡتَحَقَّآ إِثۡمٗا فَ‍َٔاخَرَانِ يَقُومَانِ مَقَامَهُمَا مِنَ </div><div>ٱلَّذِينَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱسۡتَحَقَّ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَلَيۡهِمُ <a data-content='الأقربان إلى الميت الوارثان له' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ٱلۡأَوۡلَيَٰنِ</a> فَيُقۡسِمَانِ بِٱللَّهِ لَشَهَٰدَتُنَآ أَحَقُّ </div><div>مِن</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>شَهَٰدَتِهِمَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَمَا ٱعۡتَدَيۡنَآ إِنَّآ إِذٗا لَّمِنَ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ ٧٠١ ذَٰلِكَ </div><div>أَدۡنَىٰٓ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَن</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يَأۡتُواْ بِٱلشَّهَٰدَةِ عَلَىٰ وَجۡهِهَآ أَوۡ يَخَافُوٓاْ أَن تُرَدَّ أَيۡمَٰنُۢ </div><div>بَعۡدَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَيۡمَٰنِهِمۡۗ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَٱتَّقُواْ ٱللَّهَ وَٱسۡمَعُواْۗ وَٱللَّهُ لَا يَهۡدِي ٱلۡقَوۡمَ ٱلۡفَٰسِقِينَ </div><div>٨٠١</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
